score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:26:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d521e970e93b2df37b52ab890c467c24648e02d9","tid":146273,"uid":4070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:30:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"56d4a59a5f10d69a6726580778eb69ed766ba948","tid":146273,"uid":70264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:33:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌尻啲人繁忙時間玩手機仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚似每秒幾百萬上落咁阻撚住啲位</blockquote><br />\n呢個真 其實心靈空虛</blockquote><br />\n唔望手機，唔通你眼望我眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港人每日要成粒鐘時間通勤，唔用手機浪費晒啲時間，撳手機基本上係必要，可以做嘅只係係有人流動個陣，停一停顧及其他人，港鐵使用者之間互相尊重及協調，輪唔到港鐵理。呢家港鐵連背囊手機啲雞毛蒜皮事都要理，延伸緊佢嘅權力，遲下可能叫埋人企直啲，坐直啲，行快啲。"},{"pid":"02342f938bb3c28093b799134222930adc86e832","tid":146273,"uid":70264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:36:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>根本就係香港太多人<br />\n理論上港鐵應該加價令到少啲人<br />\n但又會畀人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw水貨先係仆街仔</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港太多人係咪要瘋狂推高樓價，令到香港冇咁多人？</blockquote><br />\n如果港鐵係奢侈品，我同意，但係港鐵係必需品，價格係需要受規管。"},{"pid":"636b18e905b526c384afafcb1a75f9b485103300","tid":146273,"uid":31423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:39:03.000Z","msg":"最仆街係有班港豬自己唔孭就覺得好<br />\n又一次離間成功"},{"pid":"91a5047df0ffe885befab4404f63357f79ba1779","tid":146273,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:42:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最仆街係有班港豬自己唔孭就覺得好<br />\n又一次離間成功</blockquote><br />\n隔離POST已經有一個"},{"pid":"2c405c7a904ad43eff70fa7e1ac9e49733850688","tid":146273,"uid":22486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:42:49.000Z","msg":"世界大戰<img s